Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:48.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,黑港城的城墙……\N{\fs40}...the wall Blackhaven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:51.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,由玄武岩筑成 高不可攀\N{\fs40}are unscalable basalt stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:58.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,城堡四周由一条干涸的深沟环绕\N{\fs40}And the castle is surrounded by a deep, dry moat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:02.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,即使未来多恩入侵 城堡也绝对坚不可破\N{\fs40}It is well fortified against any future Dornish incursions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:08.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,虽然我的宝座略小\N{\fs40}And though my seat may be lesser in size,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:12.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但城堡位置优越\N{\fs40}it is situated most pleasingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:40.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我和父亲曾有幸接待过亚莉珊王后\N{\fs40}The view across the Marches is inspiring,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:44.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当时她说 边疆地的景色十分震撼人心\N{\fs40}so said Queen Alysanne herself when she honored my father and I--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:47.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,告诉我 唐德利恩大人\N{\fs40}And tell me, Lord Dondarrion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您觉得我的曾祖母有世人说得那么美丽吗？\N{\fs40}did you think my great-grandmother as beautiful as they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:56.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 那已经是半个世纪前的事了\N{\fs40}This was half a century ago, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的 的确\N{\fs40}Yes, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这话恐怕不太得体 公主\N{\fs40}That was unseemly, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:05.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这个人比我的父亲还老\N{\fs40}The man is older than my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还争着想成为我的夫婿\N{\fs40}It's unseemly for him to put himself forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这才是真的不得体\N{\fs40}as a contender for my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:12.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,下一位！\N{\fs40}Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,又来了个小孩\N{\fs40}And now a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:29.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,布莱伍德是一个古老的家族 有着强大的军事力量\N{\fs40}The Blackwoods are an ancient house with a formidable army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:34.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们曾在河间地称王统治\N{\fs40}In the Riverlands, they once ruled as kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:38.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,先民之血依旧流淌在他们体内\N{\fs40}The blood of the First Men still flows in their veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\fs40}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主殿下……\N{\fs40}My Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自从我祖父的祖父 卢卡斯·布莱伍德\N{\fs40}ours is a bond that has long endured,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:50.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在征服战争中为龙王效力以来\N{\fs40}since Lucas Blackwood, the grandsire of my grandsire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们两家的深厚情谊传承已久\N{\fs40}aided the Dragon in his war of conquest--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:55.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是呀 布莱伍德家族真是在战场上扭转乾坤了呢\N{\fs40}Aye, the Blackwoods truly turned the tide on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们历史悠久 融合了先民血脉\N{\fs40}Coursed with the blood of the First Men,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,深深扎根在这片土地上\N{\fs40}our history is deeply rooted in this land,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,正是您的家族令我们能在此安居乐业\N{\fs40}which your house has made its home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 如果我被选为您的夫婿……\N{\fs40}If chosen as your match, Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您的生活将会无比轻松\N{\fs40}your days shall be easy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:13.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也将保护您日夜周全\N{\fs40}and nights safe under my protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“保护”？公主可是有一条龙的 你这蠢货\N{\fs40}"Protection"? The Princess has a dragon, you dumb cunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:21.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,布雷肯！\N{\fs40}Bracken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这小子我倒是有点喜欢\N{\fs40}I could learn to like that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我们有请下一位吧\N{\fs40}Let us have the next
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,赶快结束就能去吃晚饭了\N{\fs40}so we may go to supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,懦夫\N{\fs40}Craven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\fs40}We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:40.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把剑收起来 你们这群蠢材！\N{\fs40}Sheathe that steel, you twats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,通知码头 让奥斯温船长把船准备好\N{\fs40}Send word to the harbor and have Captain Oswin ready the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 我们应该在三天后再去苦桥的\N{\fs40}Princess, we're due in Bitterbridge in three days' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只要能结束这荒唐的选夫大会\N{\fs40}I would happily row myself back to King's Landing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我非常乐意自己划船回君临\N{\fs40}if it brought an end to this ridiculous pageant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:55.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别看 公主\N{\fs40}Don't look, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:20.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 我们一小时内就可以登岸了\N{\fs40}We should make landfall inside the hour, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你觉得他会怎么想？\N{\fs40}How do you think he will take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您是说拒绝陛下派来的所有求亲者\N{\fs40}Do you speak of how you rejected every suitor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是说突然结束这场原本\N{\fs40}His Grace put before you, or how you abruptly ended the tour
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:30.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还剩两个月的巡游呢？\N{\fs40}with two months remaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,隐蔽！\N{\fs40}Take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:54.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主！\N{\fs40}Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:58.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您还好吗？没事吧？\N{\fs40}You all right? Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 快把学士找来！ - 我没事\N{\fs40}- Fetch the maester! - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是戴蒙\N{\fs40}It's Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:01.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把它加到王座里吧\N{\fs40}Add it to the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你戴了一顶王冠\N{\fs40}You wear a crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你自立为王了吗？\N{\fs40}Do you also call yourself "King"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们战胜三城同盟会后\N{\fs40}Once we smashed the Triarchy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:26.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们称我为“狭海之王”\N{\fs40}they named me "King of the Narrow Sea."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:34.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我明白 陛下您才是唯一真正的国王\N{\fs40}But I know that there is only one true king, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:47.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的王冠以及石阶列岛……都属于您\N{\fs40}My crown and the Stepstones... are yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯大人在哪里？\N{\fs40}Where is Lord Corlys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他驾船回潮头岛了\N{\fs40}He sailed home to Driftmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:58.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 那是谁在据守石阶列岛呢？ - 潮水……\N{\fs40}- Who holds the Stepstones? - The tides...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:04.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,螃蟹 以及两千死去的三城同盟会海盗\N{\fs40}the crabs, and 2,000 dead Triarchy corsairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:07.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我将他们曝尸沙滩 以儆效尤\N{\fs40}staked to the sand to warn those who might follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:46.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,起来吧\N{\fs40}Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:12.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王国欠你一笔大大的封赏 弟弟\N{\fs40}The realm owes you a great debt, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:16.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs40}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是我们的好机会……\N{\fs40}This is our chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙 他会外出探险 海外游历\N{\fs40}Daemon, he would venture off, abroad,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,赢下比武大会……\N{\fs40}winning tournaments...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不不不不\N{\fs40}No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不会再争论这个话题了\N{\fs40}I will not revisit this debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你一直都是母亲的最爱\N{\fs40}You were always mother's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 这不是什么了不起的大秘密\N{\fs40}No, it's no great mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你一直是她的最爱\N{\fs40}You were.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:47.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的母亲 她才不管什么习俗 传统或是规矩\N{\fs40}Our mother, she had no regard for custom or tradition, rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:50.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可惜啊 我并不是什么武艺高超的勇士\N{\fs40}And I, sadly, was no great warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:53.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恭喜您大获全胜\N{\fs40}Congratulations on your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢您 公主\N{\fs40}Thank you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许戴蒙王子想去长廊转转吗？\N{\fs40}Perhaps Prince Daemon would care for a tour of the gallery?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他还没有见过诺佛斯和科霍尔\N{\fs40}He hasn't yet seen the new tapestries
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:13.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给您送来的新挂毯呢\N{\fs40}gifted to you by Norvos and Qohor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:17.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你想去看看新挂毯吗？\N{\fs40}Would you like to see the tapestries?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:23.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他对这些东西才不感兴趣\N{\fs40}He has no interest in such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:25.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我挺想去看看\N{\fs40}I'd like to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:30.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你不用拦着自己\N{\fs40}Then you should not deprive yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那我自己去欣赏了\N{\fs40}I shall enjoy them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,倒酒\N{\fs40}More wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:45.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我说了 你才是母亲的最爱\N{\fs40}As I said, you were the favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:48.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 你是 你才是 我坚信\N{\fs40}No, you were. You were. I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:06.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我猜巡游不怎么顺利\N{\fs40}I surmise the tour did not go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经尽力忍了很久了\N{\fs40}I endured it for as long as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:14.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七国上下每一个年轻的骑士和贵族都来讨好你……\N{\fs40}To have every young knight and lord in the Seven Kingdoms fawning over you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:15.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这可真惨啊\N{\fs40}What misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对于全国女孩来说 能在两个提亲者当中选择就很难得了\N{\fs40}It is rare for girls in this realm to get a choice between two suitors,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,更不用说有四十个能挑的\N{\fs40}no less two score of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:29.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那些男人和男孩并不是想讨好我\N{\fs40}Those men and boys don't fawn over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们只是奔着我的名号和瓦雷利亚血统来的\N{\fs40}They only want my name and my Valyrian blood for their offspring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我倒觉得还挺浪漫的\N{\fs40}I think it's rather romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:42.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,关在城堡里 被逼着生出子嗣\N{\fs40}How romantic it must be to get imprisoned in a castle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:44.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还真挺浪漫\N{\fs40}and made to squeeze out heirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:50.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs40}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:02.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他有多生气？\N{\fs40}How angry is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下花了很大心思为你安排这次巡游\N{\fs40}The King went through great effort to arrange your tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:11.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他很……沮丧\N{\fs40}He is... frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过你回家了 我很高兴\N{\fs40}But I am glad you are home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:21.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我发现自己现在已经没什么朋友了\N{\fs40}I find I have few friends lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:25.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我多希望现在我还是阿莉森小姐 不过……\N{\fs40}I like to believe I'm still the Lady Alicent, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:31.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在所有人眼里 我都只是“王后陛下”\N{\fs40}all anyone sees when they look at me now is "The Queen."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:36.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也想你了\N{\fs40}I've missed you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:12.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以……\N{\fs40}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:14.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你想要什么？\N{\fs40}what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只想回归家庭温暖\N{\fs40}Only the comforts of home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:29.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我以为你在这个家里感受不到什么温暖\N{\fs40}I had not thought you particularly comfortable in this home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:36.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过我觉得 这次冒险之后你好像变了\N{\fs40}Though I do suppose you seem changed by your adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:39.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许 变得更成熟了\N{\fs40}More mature, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:44.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你这四年也成熟了许多 公主\N{\fs40}You've matured yourself these last four years, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你会习惯众人瞩目的\N{\fs40}You'll get used to the attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,受人关注我可以忍受\N{\fs40}The attention I can endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,忍不了是别的事\N{\fs40}It's the rest I could do without.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我父亲似乎很想把我卖给拥有最大城堡的领主\N{\fs40}My father seems content to sell me off
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不管是谁 只要城堡够大他就满足了\N{\fs40}to whichever lord has the biggest castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:15:00.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不知道可能还有更糟糕的交易呢\N{\fs40}There are worse things to be sold for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,听起来多么孤独啊\N{\fs40}Such a lonely prospect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:25.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,赢回石阶列岛本该归还王国所有\N{\fs40}The Stepstones were meant to be won for the realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但这么多天过去了 我们似乎只是\N{\fs40}but over the past few days, it seems we have traded
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把螃蟹喂食者换成了海蛇\N{\fs40}a crabfeeder for a seasnake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:34.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他明显是在报复您迎娶阿莉森王后 拒绝兰娜尔小姐\N{\fs40}This is clearly a rebuke for passing over Lady Laena for Queen Alicent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他为女儿求亲那件事 已经过去了好几年\N{\fs40}Years have passed since the business with his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他不会还在耿耿于怀吧？\N{\fs40}Certainly, he cannot still be wroth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:43.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问  “海蛇”过于自负 陛下\N{\fs40}The Sea Snake is an over-proud man, to be sure, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,之前的请求被拒 有损他的自尊心\N{\fs40}That pride has been injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许我们可以设法弥合伤口？\N{\fs40}Perhaps we can salve the wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:51.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恐怕科利斯大人的自尊是眼下最不需要操心的事\N{\fs40}I fear Lord Corlys's pride is the least of our worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无意给您带来更多困扰 陛下\N{\fs40}I don't wish to cause you further distress,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:57.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我哥哥从旧镇送来一条令人不安的消息\N{\fs40}Your Grace, but my brother has sent disturbing word from Oldtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:01.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,据称 科利斯伯爵正在密谋\N{\fs40}Lord Corlys is said to have engaged in negotiations
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:03.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,与布拉佛斯海王商谈婚事\N{\fs40}with the Sealord of Braavos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:06.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他打算把女儿兰娜尔嫁给海王之子\N{\fs40}He plans to wed his daughter Laena to the Sealord's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:12.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果瓦列利安家族与\N{\fs40}If House Velaryon entered into an alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:15.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自由贸易城邦结盟\N{\fs40}with the Free Cities
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:16.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fs40}then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:21.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们也应当善用我方资源缔结婚约\N{\fs40}we would have to seek our own marriage pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:13.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 晚安 克里斯顿爵士 - 祝您好梦 公主\N{\fs40}-Good night, Ser Criston. -Sleep well, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:35.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们要去哪儿？\N{\fs40}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,滚开 小子\N{\fs40}Fuck off, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他管我叫“小子”\N{\fs40}He called me boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你想知道自己的死法吗？孩子\N{\fs40}Do you wish to know your death, child?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:47.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我来吧\N{\fs40}Let me take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:04.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,全都退下\N{\fs40}Leave us, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:26.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的动作比她们轻柔多了\N{\fs40}You have a far kinder touch than they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:27.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我的夫君\N{\fs40}Thank you, husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:36.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在来说说伟大的铁王座\N{\fs40}And now we come to the matter of the great Iron Chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:40.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以及谁的屁股会坐上去\N{\fs40}and whose bum it might bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:42.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的好国王\N{\fs40}Our good King...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:44.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,选定了他的女儿\N{\fs40}names his daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:46.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个女孩 作为继承人\N{\fs40}a girl, his heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:54.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但后来 他又有了一个孩子\N{\fs40}But then to him, a babe is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:05.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是个儿子！\N{\fs40}A son!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:10.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谁会继承铁王座？\N{\fs40}To which heir might the chair bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:11.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会是谁？\N{\fs40}Who will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:14.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是弟弟？还是女儿？\N{\fs40}The brother? The daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.14,0:23:16.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是三岁的小王子？\N{\fs40}Or the little princeling of three?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:32.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉 王国之光\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra... the Realm's Delight,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:35.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个女孩 如此年轻 势单力薄\N{\fs40}a girl so young and so slight...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:39.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她被所有臣民爱戴\N{\fs40}loved by all of her people,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.58,0:23:43.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但她能成为强大的女王吗？\N{\fs40}but would she make a powerful queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:46.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 还是弱不禁风？- 弱不禁风！\N{\fs40}-or would she be feeble? -Feeble!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:49.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有伊耿 小王子 没准他也盯着王位\N{\fs40}Though Aegon, the babe Prince, might long for a claim,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:53.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他有两样东西 雷妮拉不能比\N{\fs40}he has two things Rhaenyra cannot:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:55.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他有征服者的名字\N{\fs40}a conqueror's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:57.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还带着把儿\N{\fs40}and a cock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:03.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谎言 诽谤！嘘！\N{\fs40}Lies, slander! Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.44,0:24:05.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就当是笑话吧\N{\fs40}Jest if you will,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.19,0:24:07.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过这些市井小民更愿意相信\N{\fs40}but many of the smallfolk are like to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.19,0:24:10.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为男性 伊耿应当成为继承人\N{\fs40}that, as a male, Aegon should be the heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.90,0:24:13.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,随便他们怎么想 不重要\N{\fs40}Their wants are of no consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:20.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你日后想要统治这群人 他们怎么想就很重要\N{\fs40}They're of great consequence if you expect to rule them one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:25.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个晚上就好 我想卸下继承人的重担\N{\fs40}For one night, I wish to be free of the burdens of my inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.84,0:24:33.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,四个铜板 臭老鼠\N{\fs40}Four coppers, street rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.09,0:24:35.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在君临城 我们为自己的欢愉买单\N{\fs40}In King's Landing, we pay for our pleasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.72,0:24:38.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 喂！- 站住！小子！\N{\fs40}-Hey! -Stop! Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.18,0:24:39.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你等着 我会抓到他\N{\fs40}Wait, I'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.01,0:25:21.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你跑什么 在躲谁？\N{\fs40}And who might you be running from, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.26,0:25:22.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哈尔温爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Harwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.06,0:25:24.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主\N{\fs40}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.11,0:25:30.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请别\N{\fs40}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.32,0:25:32.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,注意点 小子\N{\fs40}You take care, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.03,0:25:35.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,下次你可就没这么幸运了\N{\fs40}Next time, you might not be so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.70,0:25:41.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,挺开心的 对吧？\N{\fs40}Enjoyed that, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.16,0:25:46.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谁知道下次品尝自由的味道 要等到什么时候\N{\fs40}Who knows when I'll next taste freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.93,0:26:00.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fs40}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.60,0:26:06.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请您原谅 王后陛下\N{\fs40}Pardon me, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.69,0:26:09.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王陛下请您过去\N{\fs40}The King has requested your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.49,0:26:16.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在很晚了\N{\fs40}The hour is quite late.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.15,0:26:18.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的 王后陛下\N{\fs40}Yes, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.49,0:28:26.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方\N{\fs40}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.49,0:28:30.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是人们满足需求的地方\N{\fs40}It's where people come to take what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.18,0:28:54.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你看 性爱也是一种欢愉\N{\fs40}Fucking is a pleasure, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.19,0:28:58.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,男女都一样\N{\fs40}For the woman as it is the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.58,0:29:15.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,婚姻是责任 没错\N{\fs40}A marriage is a duty... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.92,0:29:22.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但婚姻并不会阻止我们追求快乐\N{\fs40}But that doesn't stop us from doing what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.80,0:29:28.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,睡我们想睡的人\N{\fs40}From fucking who we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.80,0:30:50.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙？\N{\fs40}Daemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.22,0:31:31.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主？\N{\fs40}Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.93,0:31:41.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 您 您受伤了吗？\N{\fs40}Princess, are you, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.86,0:31:47.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我该通知御林铁卫队长 - 别\N{\fs40}-I should alert the Lord Commander. -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.57,0:31:56.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的头盔\N{\fs40}My helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.75,0:32:04.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您闹够了吗？\N{\fs40}You finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.21,0:32:09.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs40}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.75,0:32:41.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请停下\N{\fs40}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.70,0:36:44.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,很抱歉在深夜打扰您 大人\N{\fs40}Apologies for the late hour, my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.24,0:36:45.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\fs40}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.41,0:36:47.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,白蛆托人给您带个话\N{\fs40}A messenger brings word from the White Worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.39,0:37:15.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你把我当成犯人了吗？\N{\fs40}Am I your prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.85,0:37:18.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就像你曾经对我那样？\N{\fs40}As I was once yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.90,0:37:25.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你很幸运 我是你的保护者\N{\fs40}I'm your protector, lucky for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.75,0:37:35.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,喝了这个 可以解酒\N{\fs40}This will cut the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.88,0:37:40.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不需要一个普通的妓女来保护我\N{\fs40}I don't need protection from a common whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.59,0:37:42.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我并不普通\N{\fs40}I am not so common.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.01,0:37:46.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好吧 一个并不普通的妓女\N{\fs40}A not-so-common whore then.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.47,0:37:49.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我早已告别了那种生活\N{\fs40}I've left that life behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.10,0:37:53.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,皮肉交易能给予我的非常有限\N{\fs40}I learned that skin-trade could only take me so far in this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.23,0:37:56.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你向来不安分\N{\fs40}You never were one to stay idle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.35,0:38:00.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我并不想历经磨难 但也只能咬牙忍受\N{\fs40}Hard lessons are not welcomed but suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.75,0:38:19.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,出门时记得去付房钱\N{\fs40}You can pay for the room on your way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.23,0:38:46.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fs40}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.00,0:38:57.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\fs40}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.87,0:39:01.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 万分抱歉 一大早就打扰您\N{\fs40}I apologize for the early hour, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.38,0:39:03.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我有\N{\fs40}I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.05,0:39:06.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有些让人不安的消息\N{\fs40}discomforting news.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.34,0:39:09.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想 最好在御前会议召开前 先私下向您禀告\N{\fs40}I thought it best shared discreetly before the council convenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.72,0:39:11.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是海蛇吗\N{\fs40}The Sea Snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.81,0:39:17.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 恐怕此事和公主有关\N{\fs40}I'm afraid it concerns the Princess, my King.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.44,0:39:20.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她受到伤害了？\N{\fs40}Has she been harmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.19,0:39:27.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把女儿的一些事情告知父亲\N{\fs40}It is no easy thing
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.65,0:39:30.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,并非易事\N{\fs40}to tell a father of his daughter's exploits.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.82,0:39:33.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也想保持沉默 但是——\N{\fs40}I had considered saying nothing, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.95,0:39:35.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她做了什么？\N{\fs40}What has she done?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.04,0:39:41.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,昨晚 有人见到公主\N{\fs40}The Princess was spied last evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.00,0:39:45.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在红堡外的\N{\fs40}beyond the walls of the Keep...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.25,0:39:48.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一所妓院里\N{\fs40}in a pleasure house.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.42,0:39:50.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你说什么？\N{\fs40}What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.30,0:39:54.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她和她的叔叔搞在一起\N{\fs40}She was carrying on with her uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.85,0:40:00.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们的所作所为 有损公主的\N{\fs40}They were engaged in behaviors unbecoming of a maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.10,0:40:03.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,贞洁之名\N{\fs40}of a Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.94,0:40:08.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么所作所为\N{\fs40}What behaviors?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.70,0:40:16.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我必须明说吗 陛下\N{\fs40}Well, must I say it, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.74,0:40:20.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你走进我的寝宫 指责我的女儿 又不把话说清\N{\fs40}You enter my bedchamber, accusing my daughter of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.16,0:40:22.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你直接点吧\N{\fs40}Now speak it... plainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.50,0:40:29.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有人看见戴蒙和雷妮拉在一起\N{\fs40}Daemon and Rhaenyra were seen together...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.84,0:40:32.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在妓院深处\N{\fs40}in the bowels of a pleasure den.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.23,0:40:45.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他睡了她\N{\fs40}Coupling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.57,0:40:55.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,胡说八道\N{\fs40}This is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.20,0:40:57.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你被骗了\N{\fs40}You have been lied to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.83,0:41:00.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也希望是这样 陛下\N{\fs40}I only wish that were true, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.04,0:41:05.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是谁在传播谣言？\N{\fs40}Who is responsible for this gossip?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.21,0:41:08.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,立刻把这个造谣的带来见我\N{\fs40}Have this rumormonger brought before me at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.75,0:41:10.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要挖掉他的眼睛\N{\fs40}And I will take their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.84,0:41:14.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为首相 收集可靠情报是我职责所在\N{\fs40}As your Hand, I must maintain trusted sources of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.51,0:41:17.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这次的眼线非常可靠 至今从未失手\N{\fs40}And this one, as yet, has never led me astray.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.97,0:41:21.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,并且 好几个仆人已经承认\N{\fs40}And several of the servants have now admitted to seeing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.39,0:41:22.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,见到公主……\N{\fs40}the Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.52,0:41:25.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在猫头鹰时\N{\fs40}creeping through the gates from King's Landing,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.77,0:41:27.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,乔装成侍从\N{\fs40}disguised as a page
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.73,0:41:29.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,偷偷溜过君临城门\N{\fs40}during the hour of the owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.32,0:41:33.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你被野心冲昏了头脑是吧\N{\fs40}Are you so sick with ambition
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.57,0:41:35.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,居然派人跟踪我女儿？\N{\fs40}that you would have my daughter stalked?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.07,0:41:37.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,秘密监视她？\N{\fs40}Spied upon?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.28,0:41:41.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就等着绝佳机会 好毁掉她的名誉是吧？\N{\fs40}Awaiting your best chance to destroy her reputation?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.33,0:41:45.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我绝无此意 陛下\N{\fs40}I have no such intent, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.21,0:41:47.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你自以为很聪明\N{\fs40}You think yourself a cunning man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.33,0:41:49.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你那些心思也太明显了吧\N{\fs40}Your designs are obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.50,0:41:53.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你就那么想把你的血脉推上铁王座\N{\fs40}Do you wish to have your blood on the Iron Throne so badly
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.92,0:41:56.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,甚至不惜毁掉我的血脉？\N{\fs40}that you are willing to destroy mine own?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.76,0:41:59.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\fs40}Just get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.02,0:42:06.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,立刻给我出去\N{\fs40}Leave me... at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.94,0:42:13.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 告退\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.73,0:42:56.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我穿好衣服了 阿诺拉 进来吧\N{\fs40}I'm dressed, Annora. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.95,0:43:07.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主\N{\fs40}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.92,0:43:13.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fs40}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.76,0:43:26.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 王后让我过来传个话\N{\fs40}Princess, I have a message from the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.04,0:43:52.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,昨晚发生了什么？\N{\fs40}What happened last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.50,0:43:56.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么意思？\N{\fs40}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.55,0:43:59.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我父亲对你提出了一些令人担忧的指控\N{\fs40}My father has made some worrying allegations about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.18,0:44:03.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你当时是和你叔叔在一起吗？\N{\fs40}Were you with your uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.93,0:44:07.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哦 我……\N{\fs40}Oh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.02,0:44:09.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我好几年没见过他了\N{\fs40}I haven't seen him in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.81,0:44:11.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他带我到城里去放松一下\N{\fs40}He took me into the city for some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.35,0:44:13.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,全都告诉我 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}Tell me the whole of it, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.69,0:44:15.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你父亲指控我做了什么\N{\fs40}Your father accused me of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.73,0:44:18.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,喝酒吗？\N{\fs40}That I drank wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.82,0:44:21.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是天黑以后离开城堡？\N{\fs40}Left the castle after dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.32,0:44:23.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在妓院睡了戴蒙\N{\fs40}That you fucked Daemon in a pleasure house.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.00,0:44:36.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这真是个卑鄙的指控\N{\fs40}This is a vile accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.34,0:44:37.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fs40}Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.46,0:44:40.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们坦格利安确实有一些奇怪的传统\N{\fs40}You Targaryens do have queer customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.46,0:44:43.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 而且戴蒙显然毫无底线 - 阿莉森\N{\fs40}-And Daemon certainly knows no limit. -Alicent...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.72,0:44:46.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后陛下 姐姐 你一定要相信我\N{\fs40}Your Grace, sister, you must know I would,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.39,0:44:47.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我绝不会\N{\fs40}I would never.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.81,0:44:49.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不能这样轻信谣言\N{\fs40}You cannot believe such gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.35,0:44:50.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我父亲所说不是谣言\N{\fs40}My father is no gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.64,0:44:51.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,很显然他被误导了\N{\fs40}Well, certainly he's been misled.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.89,0:44:53.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这种事他不可能亲眼目睹\N{\fs40}He could not have witnessed such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.27,0:44:54.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 为什么？ - 因为这事纯属捏造\N{\fs40}-Why not? -Because it did not happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.02,0:44:56.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 有人告诉他——  - 有人？\N{\fs40}-He was told that you-- -Told?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.48,0:45:01.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谁对你父亲说的这些？\N{\fs40}Who made these claims to your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.36,0:45:07.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是公主\N{\fs40}I am the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.08,0:45:10.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,质疑我的品德就是叛国行为\N{\fs40}To question my virtue is an act of treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.41,0:45:16.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我并不知道具体—— - 你父亲没有告诉你吗？\N{\fs40}-I do not know specifically-- -Your father did not tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.83,0:45:18.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他向国王报告此事\N{\fs40}He reported it to the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.63,0:45:22.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我听到了\N{\fs40}I overheard.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.84,0:45:29.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以你用无意听到的诽谤……\N{\fs40}So you are accusing me of slanders...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.26,0:45:31.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来指责我？\N{\fs40}you overheard?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.68,0:45:34.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只想帮助你 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}I only want to help you, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.44,0:45:45.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们去了一家酒馆喝酒\N{\fs40}We drank in a tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.91,0:45:49.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,几家……酒馆\N{\fs40}Several... taverns.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.62,0:45:52.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,后来太晚了……\N{\fs40}It was getting late...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.16,0:45:54.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要回家\N{\fs40}and I asked to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.79,0:45:57.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但戴蒙还想继续\N{\fs40}But Daemon wished to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.50,0:46:02.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是跟着他出去的 决定权不在我\N{\fs40}As he was my escort, I had no real choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.05,0:46:04.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“继续”……\N{\fs40}"Continue"...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.05,0:46:08.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在妓院吗？\N{\fs40}in a brothel?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.01,0:46:11.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他带我去看了一场表演\N{\fs40}He took me to a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.14,0:46:16.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只是观看 什么都没做\N{\fs40}I was only a spectator. I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.69,0:46:24.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然后戴蒙喝得烂醉\N{\fs40}And then Daemon sank into his cups and
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.20,0:46:29.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就丢下我去找妓女了\N{\fs40}abandoned me for some whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.33,0:46:36.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我早该知道的\N{\fs40}I should've known better.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.42,0:46:43.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以你并没有？\N{\fs40}So you did not?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.88,0:46:49.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真的需要我正式否认吗？\N{\fs40}Must I truly refute that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.39,0:46:55.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙没有碰过我\N{\fs40}Daemon never touched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.60,0:47:01.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我以我母亲的名义发誓\N{\fs40}I swear this to you upon the memory of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.23,0:47:07.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把自己置于这样清白会受到质疑的境地\N{\fs40}It was foolish of you to place yourself in a position
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.32,0:47:09.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你真是太蠢了\N{\fs40}where your virtue could even come into question.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.53,0:47:15.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下竭尽全力为你寻找良配\N{\fs40}The King has strived to find you a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.58,0:47:16.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也一样\N{\fs40}And so have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.87,0:47:20.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果那位大人认为你被……\N{\fs40}If that lord were to think that you had been...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.88,0:47:23.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,玷污了……\N{\fs40}sullied...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.75,0:47:27.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 那一切都毁了 - 我知道……\N{\fs40}-it would ruin everything. -I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.97,0:47:28.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.97,0:47:32.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很后悔\N{\fs40}I regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.69,0:47:49.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王命你觐见 王子殿下\N{\fs40}The King demands an audience, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.99,0:47:52.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把你的脏手拿开\N{\fs40}Take your fucking hands off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.50,0:48:41.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我女儿\N{\fs40}My daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.17,0:48:51.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你都不否认一下吗？\N{\fs40}Won't you even deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.84,0:48:55.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我得先知道罪名 才能知道要否认什么\N{\fs40}I need to understand the charge before I can attempt to discredit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.01,0:48:58.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你玷污了她\N{\fs40}You defiled her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.11,0:49:08.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你还是什么都不说\N{\fs40}Still, you say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.69,0:49:10.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有什么关系呢 哥哥？\N{\fs40}What does it matter, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.07,0:49:12.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们在雷妮拉这个年龄的时候\N{\fs40}When we were Rhaenyra's age,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.40,0:49:14.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可是把丝绸街的那些妓院\N{\fs40}we fucked our way through most of the brothels
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.36,0:49:15.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一路干了个遍\N{\fs40}on the Street of Silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.91,0:49:17.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们是年轻男人\N{\fs40}We were young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.95,0:49:19.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而她只是个小女孩\N{\fs40}She is just a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.95,0:49:22.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你的侄女！ - 雷妮拉是个成年女子了\N{\fs40}-Your niece! -Rhaenyra's a woman-grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.25,0:49:24.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,比起我们是跟几个婊子 她的第一次跟我还不错吧\N{\fs40}Better her first experience be with me than some whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.75,0:49:25.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你他妈的——\N{\fs40}You fucking--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.46,0:49:29.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你毁了她！\N{\fs40}You have ruined her!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.80,0:49:31.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,到了这个地步  哪位大人还会娶她？\N{\fs40}What lord will wed her now? In this condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.05,0:49:34.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谁他妈在意什么大人怎么想？\N{\fs40}Who gives a fuck what some lord thinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.68,0:49:38.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是真龙 你的话就是金科玉律\N{\fs40}You are the dragon. Your word is truth and law.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.85,0:49:41.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一辈子都在维护你\N{\fs40}I have spent a lifetime defending you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.93,0:49:44.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你的心比我想的还要黑\N{\fs40}But your heart is even blacker than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.48,0:49:48.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我应该废掉她的继承权 就像当初对你一样 一了百了\N{\fs40}I should disinherit her as I already did you and be done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.98,0:49:51.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把她嫁给我\N{\fs40}Wed her to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.11,0:49:56.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当我献上王冠时 你说我要什么都可以的\N{\fs40}When I offered up my crown, you said I could have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.41,0:49:58.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要雷妮拉 我会接受这样的她\N{\fs40}I want Rhaenyra. I'll take her as she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.78,0:50:00.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,按我们的家族传统娶了她\N{\fs40}and wed her in the tradition of our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.83,0:50:03.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你已经结婚了\N{\fs40}You are already wed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.20,0:50:05.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,征服者伊耿也娶了第二位妻子啊\N{\fs40}That didn't stop Aegon the Conqueror from taking a second wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.62,0:50:08.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不是征服者\N{\fs40}You are no conqueror.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.33,0:50:11.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你就是……我命中灾星\N{\fs40}You are a plague... sent to destroy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.88,0:50:14.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我娶雷妮拉为妻\N{\fs40}Give me Rhaenyra to take to wife
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.88,0:50:18.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们会让龙王家族恢复往日荣光\N{\fs40}and we will return the House of the Dragon to its proper glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.72,0:50:19.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\fs40}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.05,0:50:22.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你觊觎的并非我的女儿 是吗？\N{\fs40}It's not my daughter you lust for, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.60,0:50:24.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而是我的王位\N{\fs40}It's my throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.44,0:50:29.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,回谷地去 戴蒙\N{\fs40}Go back to the Vale, Daemon,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.02,0:50:31.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,到你的合法妻子身边去\N{\fs40}to your lawful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.94,0:50:37.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,努力去重建你身上残存的荣誉吧\N{\fs40}Strive to restore whatever scrap of honor remains in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.99,0:50:40.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不去也行 我不在乎\N{\fs40}Or don't. Matters not to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.53,0:50:43.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只要永远别让我再看见你\N{\fs40}As long as you are gone from my sight for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.33,0:50:53.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如你所愿 哥哥\N{\fs40}As you wish, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.49,0:51:25.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和她谈过了吗\N{\fs40}Have you spoken to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.83,0:51:28.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.17,0:51:36.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉天性耿直 她不会撒谎\N{\fs40}It is not in Rhaenyra's nature to be deceitful.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.05,0:51:39.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您的弟弟却未必如此\N{\fs40}I cannot say the same for your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.97,0:51:42.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你认为他撒谎了？\N{\fs40}You believe he lied?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.55,0:51:45.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他说过几句纯粹的真话？\N{\fs40}How often does he speak the pure truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.10,0:51:50.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,承认这种事情 对他有什么好处？\N{\fs40}How does confessing to such things serve him?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.98,0:51:54.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可以削弱您的权威\N{\fs40}By reducing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.99,0:52:04.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无论发生了什么 雷妮拉也不清白\N{\fs40}Whatever transpired, Rhaenyra is not innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.41,0:52:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是因为戴蒙引诱她堕落\N{\fs40}Only because Daemon tried to corrupt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.91,0:52:11.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙和雷妮拉都流着真龙之血\N{\fs40}Daemon and Rhaenyra share the blood of the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.25,0:52:13.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们反复无常 从不安分\N{\fs40}They are restless and chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.12,0:52:15.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她向我发誓她仍是处子之身\N{\fs40}She swore to me that she remains a maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.59,0:52:19.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我相信她\N{\fs40}And I believe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.40,0:53:26.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这把匕首 曾为征服者伊耿所有\N{\fs40}That dagger once belonged to Aegon the Conqueror.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.62,0:53:30.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,往上可以追溯到伊纳尔\N{\fs40}It was Aenar's before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.45,0:53:33.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,再往前……\N{\fs40}And before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.91,0:53:35.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就说不清了\N{\fs40}It is difficult to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.59,0:53:45.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿去世前 瓦雷利亚最后的火术士\N{\fs40}Before Aegon's death, the last of the Valyrian pyromancers
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.63,0:53:47.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,将他的歌藏在刀刃上\N{\fs40}hid his song in the steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.85,0:53:56.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“我的血脉中……”\N{\fs40}"From my blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.60,0:54:00.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“将诞生预言中的王子……“\N{\fs40}"come the Prince That Was Promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.94,0:54:06.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“他的血便是冰与火之歌”\N{\fs40}and his will be the Song of Ice and Fire."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.95,0:54:14.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我交付给你的责任\N{\fs40}The responsibility I have handed to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.50,0:54:16.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,知晓此事的负担\N{\fs40}the burden of this knowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.87,0:54:21.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,远比王位和国王更重要\N{\fs40}it is larger than the throne, the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.46,0:54:23.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,远比你和你的欲望\N{\fs40}It is larger than you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.09,0:54:25.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,更重要\N{\fs40}and your desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.80,0:54:32.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果是杰赫里斯 他会剥夺你的继承权\N{\fs40}Jaehaerys would've disinherited you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.35,0:54:33.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就因为一个谎言？\N{\fs40}For a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.93,0:54:37.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你甚至都没问我 真相到底是什么\N{\fs40}You've yet to ask me for the truth of what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.69,0:54:40.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真相不重要 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}The truth does not matter, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.27,0:54:42.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,世人的看法才重要\N{\fs40}Only perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.23,0:54:43.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你将自己置于危险境地\N{\fs40}You have exposed yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.07,0:54:46.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如今我们都得承担后果\N{\fs40}Now we must both suffer the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.65,0:54:49.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,假如生为男子 那我想睡谁就能睡谁\N{\fs40}Were I born a man, I could bed whomever I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.62,0:54:52.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可以生一打私生子女\N{\fs40}I could father a dozen bastards,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.37,0:54:55.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你朝堂上那些人连眼睛都不会眨一下\N{\fs40}and no one in your court would blink an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.16,0:54:58.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你说的没错……但谁让你生为女子\N{\fs40}You are right... but you were born a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.42,0:55:02.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以你就要剥夺我的头衔 转而立伊耿为嗣\N{\fs40}So you'll strip me of my titles and name Aegon in my stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.21,0:55:03.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也想这样\N{\fs40}I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.42,0:55:08.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我的职责 是将王国团结一心 而不是制造更多分裂\N{\fs40}But it is mine to hold the realm together, not sow it with further division.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.43,0:55:13.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你选择夫婿的自由到此为止\N{\fs40}Your courtship is at an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.14,0:55:15.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,接下来 你将会嫁给兰尼诺·瓦列利安爵士\N{\fs40}You will wed Ser Laenor Velaryon,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.43,0:55:17.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不得有违\N{\fs40}and you will do so without protest.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.89,0:55:20.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海蛇之子\N{\fs40}The son of the Sea Snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.94,0:55:23.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就这样拿我来治你的政治顽疾\N{\fs40}So I can be a remedy for your political headaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.52,0:55:26.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你就是我的政治顽疾！\N{\fs40}You are my political headache!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.61,0:55:32.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你嫁给兰尼诺·瓦列利安\N{\fs40}Your wedding to Ser Laenor Velaryon
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.95,0:55:35.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会将王国最有权势的两大家族团结起来\N{\fs40}will unite the two most powerful houses in the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.87,0:55:39.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一旦我们的巨龙与舰队联合起来\N{\fs40}With the combined strength of our shared dragons and naval fleets,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.96,0:55:42.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就无人胆敢发起挑战\N{\fs40}no one would dare to stand against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.71,0:55:44.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙王家族\N{\fs40}The House of the Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.13,0:55:46.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,将团结一心 延绵至下个世代\N{\fs40}will stand as one for a further generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.67,0:55:50.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你会怎么处置停在王座上的秃鹫？\N{\fs40}And what will you do about the vulture who perches upon your throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.01,0:55:52.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么秃鹫？\N{\fs40}What vulture?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.97,0:55:54.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的首相\N{\fs40}Your Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.89,0:55:59.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,奥托·海塔尔忠心耿耿地侍奉了两代国王\N{\fs40}Otto Hightower has served two kings loyally and faithfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.27,0:56:03.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他想让伊耿当王储\N{\fs40}He wants Aegon to be named heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.90,0:56:06.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不达目的 他不会罢休\N{\fs40}And he will stop at nothing to see it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.57,0:56:09.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,比如 为了毁掉我而监视我\N{\fs40}Including spying on me to bring about my ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.99,0:56:13.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你口口声声说着征服者的预言\N{\fs40}You speak of The Conqueror's vision
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.66,0:56:16.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说着需要力量 说着团结王国\N{\fs40}and the need for strength and unity across the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.99,0:56:18.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但如果你最信任的谋臣一心只为个人私利\N{\fs40}But how can that be accomplished
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.70,0:56:21.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你又怎能实现这一切？\N{\fs40}with your most trusted adviser so self-interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.33,0:56:23.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,外面请求觐见的每位领主和贵妇\N{\fs40}Every lord and lady that calls for an audience with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.88,0:56:25.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的御前重臣 乃至历代所有御前重臣\N{\fs40}every man on my small council,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.79,0:56:28.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,人人自利 谁能例外\N{\fs40}and all councils past, has been self-interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.84,0:56:31.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 这是人的天性 - 我不同意\N{\fs40}- It is unavoidable. - I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.38,0:56:35.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会履行王储的职责 嫁给兰尼诺爵士\N{\fs40}I will do my duty as heir and wed Ser Laenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.89,0:56:40.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但首先 你要履行国王的职责\N{\fs40}But you must first do yours as king.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.15,0:56:53.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.87,0:56:56.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,五天\N{\fs40}Five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.41,0:57:02.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,抱歉 陛下？\N{\fs40}I'm sorry, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.46,0:57:04.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是很多年前了\N{\fs40}Though it was some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.87,0:57:07.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,很多细节……已然消失在记忆中\N{\fs40}The details... they fade in memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.92,0:57:12.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的父亲曾是一位健壮的战士和驭龙者\N{\fs40}My father was a hale and healthy warrior and dragonrider
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.38,0:57:14.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当时他正值壮年\N{\fs40}at the peak of his abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.09,0:57:16.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杰赫里斯举办了盛大的王家围猎\N{\fs40}Jaehaerys named a great royal hunt
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.89,0:57:19.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来庆祝他担任首相\N{\fs40}to celebrate him being named the Hand of the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.27,0:57:24.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,五天之后 我的父亲死了\N{\fs40}Five days later my father lay dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.69,0:57:28.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就连比武大会都还没开完\N{\fs40}Tourneys last longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.90,0:57:32.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“勇敢的”贝尔隆\N{\fs40}Baelon the Brave,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.28,0:57:34.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦格哈尔的骑士\N{\fs40}rider of Vhagar,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.45,0:57:36.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,铁王座的继承人……\N{\fs40}heir to the Iron Throne...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.87,0:57:39.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,死于肚腹破裂\N{\fs40}dead of a burst belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.74,0:57:43.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神自有黑色的智慧\N{\fs40}The gods have a dark wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.37,0:57:46.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是残酷的一天\N{\fs40}It was a grim day.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.58,0:57:50.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我记得非常清晰 - 是啊……\N{\fs40}- I recall it all too well. - Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.21,0:57:53.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对你来说 那可是个好日子\N{\fs40}It was a good day for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.55,0:57:57.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杰赫里斯让你接替贝尔隆做了首相\N{\fs40}Jaehaerys named you Hand in Baelon's stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.51,0:58:03.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我从没这么想过 陛下\N{\fs40}That's hardly how I viewed it, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.35,0:58:05.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是责任\N{\fs40}It was a duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.73,0:58:12.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是你侍奉我的祖父度过了最后的时日\N{\fs40}You served my grandsire nobly in his final days.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.90,0:58:16.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是你教我怎么成为国王\N{\fs40}You are the man that taught me how to be King.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.11,0:58:21.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下过誉\N{\fs40}You honor me, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.29,0:58:23.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,仅仅五天……\N{\fs40}Just five days...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.62,0:58:28.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你就从杰赫里斯朝中的无名之辈\N{\fs40}you went from being another man in Jaehaerys's court,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.00,0:58:31.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一跃成为整个王国的二号人物\N{\fs40}to the second most powerful man in the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.34,0:58:33.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我在想……\N{\fs40}I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.96,0:58:37.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,选择将个人利益置于国王之上 又费得了你多少时间呢？\N{\fs40}how long did it take you to choose yourself over your King?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.80,0:58:41.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下？\N{\fs40}Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.22,0:58:45.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,爱玛之死是我永远无法治愈的伤痛\N{\fs40}I will never recover from Aemma's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.77,0:58:47.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而阿莉森……\N{\fs40}But Alicent...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.98,0:58:50.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她陪我度过了最悲伤的时候\N{\fs40}she took me through the worst of my grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.48,0:58:56.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但她的陪伴只是一场精心算计\N{\fs40}She was a calculated distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.36,0:59:00.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我现在才意识到 你算得太精妙了\N{\fs40}I only now realize how well-calculated it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.57,0:59:02.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,太荒谬了\N{\fs40}That is an absurdity.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.62,0:59:05.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后爱您……\N{\fs40}The Queen loves you...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.83,0:59:08.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,正如您也爱她\N{\fs40}as I know you love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.92,0:59:12.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的利益不再与王国一致\N{\fs40}Your interests no longer align with those of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.38,0:59:14.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的判断受了太多干扰\N{\fs40}Your judgment has been compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.84,0:59:17.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一位忠诚的首相\N{\fs40}A loyal Hand must tell his king
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.42,0:59:20.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,必然时时忠言逆耳 陛下\N{\fs40}a discomforting truth from time to time, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.64,0:59:22.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果没有做到……\N{\fs40}If he doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.64,0:59:25.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就是他的失职\N{\fs40}he's failed as a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.68,0:59:29.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是一位忠实的仆从 奥托\N{\fs40}You were a faithful servant, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.70,0:59:40.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你为国王与王国奉献良多\N{\fs40}The crown and the realm
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.66,0:59:43.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我将永远铭记\N{\fs40}both owe you a debt that can never be repaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.83,0:59:47.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我无法再信任你的判断\N{\fs40}But I can no longer trust your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.85,1:00:12.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fs40}Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.78,1:00:20.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,深夜打扰 请您原谅 公主殿下\N{\fs40}I hope you can forgive the late hour, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.66,1:00:28.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是我精心准备的\N{\fs40}I took great care in its preparation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.33,1:00:34.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果调制不当 要么失灵\N{\fs40}If not brewed properly, it can either prove ineffective
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.29,1:00:38.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 要么会有不良反应……  - 调制不当？\N{\fs40}- or else bear unpleasant-- - Brewed properly?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.21,1:00:41.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等等 这是什么？\N{\fs40}I'm sorry, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.55,1:00:44.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一种茶 公主殿下\N{\fs40}A tea, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.26,1:00:46.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是国王给您的\N{\fs40}From the King.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.89,1:00:53.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,它会让您避免任何意外的后果\N{\fs40}It will rid you of any unwanted consequences.
