Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:39.00,Note_top,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}布雷肯家族与布莱伍德家族自安达尔人入侵前便为世仇，\N布雷肯家族在安达尔人入侵后改信七神，而布莱伍德家族有着坚定的旧神信仰。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:24.00,Note_top,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}此剑为“黑火”，是坦格利安家族祖传宝剑之一，\N曾为“征服者”伊耿的佩剑。有人认为这把剑象征着王权。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.00,1:00:50.00,Note_top,,0,0,0,,{\fs50}月茶，一种用来避孕及堕胎的草药茶。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.65,0:53:33.00,Note_top,,0,0,0,,{\fs50}“流亡者”伊纳尔·坦格利安，是坦格利安王室的祖先，\N曾在末日浩劫降临瓦雷利亚之前率领整个家族迁至龙石岛。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:13.80,Note_rotation_Left_HOTD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(550,360)}穿上这个\N{\fs20}Kesommi aōle mīsās. \N\N{\fs30}推开挂毯后面的墙\N{\fs20}Rhakiāzmo inkot dōros indīs.\N\N{\fs30}沿着通道走\N{\fs20}Geltilio rȳ jās.\N\N{\fs30}我在外面等你\N{\fs20}Ninkiot avy rhaeninna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:49.30,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,你看上去在龙石岛过得很满足\N{\fs40}Hae hunē kirine Zaldrīzdōrot īlō vestretas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.56,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,为什么要回来呢？\N{\fs40}Skoro syt āmastā?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:14:00.40,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,你回来肯定不只是为了戏弄我父亲\N{\fs40}Sīlāvose umbun aōho āmāzinot kepe ñuhe mīvindigon toliot ilzi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.13,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,婚姻不过是一场政治上的安排\N{\fs40}Idīnnon dēmalio syt verdilla mērī issa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:11.05,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,结了婚以后 你可以想干什么就干什么\N{\fs40}Dīnakson toliot, gaoso gaomagon kostas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.56,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,对男人来说 婚姻或许是政治上的安排\N{\fs40}Valo syt, idīnnon dēmalio syt verdilla sagon kostus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.26,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,对女人 婚姻就像宣判死刑\N{\fs40}Ābro syt, vējītsos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:22.47,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话 我早就摆脱我那个青铜婊子了\N{\fs40}Hegnīr iksos jaelan. Nyke hen ñuho Brāedāzmo Bratsiot ēlio ono gō dāerēdoks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.24,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,你的妻子很幸运\N{\fs40}Ābrazȳrys aōhys biare istas;
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.32,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,你没有让她怀孕\N{\fs40}ziry lēdetō daor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:38.41,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,我都怀疑 那么恶劣的环境里 孩子能不能长大\N{\fs40}Keso qrinuntenko tolālȳti ūbriljagon rūs nājumban.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:49.92,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,我的母亲被逼诞下子嗣 直到这件事最后害死了她\N{\fs40}Muña ñuha dārannī āpykagon isētaks vapār ziry morghākotas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.93,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,我不会让自己也遭受同样的命运\N{\fs40}Hēnkos vējose botilun daor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:55.93,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,发生在你母亲身上的事是一场悲剧\N{\fs40}Aōhe muñe imassitas līr mundāzma istas,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.10,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,但这世界本就充满悲剧\N{\fs40}yn kesy mundāzmo vȳs issa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:09.23,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,你不能一生都活在恐惧中 那样你会错过人生最精彩的部分\N{\fs40}Glaeson aōhon zūgose glaesagon kostō daor, iā jāhī albijossa āzālilē.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.86,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,我不想活在恐惧中\N{\fs40}Zūgose glaesilun jaelon daor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.07,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,只想独自生活\N{\fs40}Mērpāvose glaesilun.